# Unit 3 Chapter 2 Project: Design a Game

Chapter 2 of Unit 3 ends with a project. In this project, students plan and build their own game using the project guide from previous lessons. This project is an opportunity for students to showcase technical skills, allow them to collaborate with a partner, provide constructive feedback, and repeatedly use the problem solving process. 

## Sample Projects

Check out some sample projects to get an idea of what students will create at the conclusion of Unit 3: Interactive Animations and Games. 

